Cocktails
MAI TAI
A fabulous South Seas potion that blends the sunny glow of rum with
the exotic flavors of tropical fruit. Sip! And dream of sunset on the reef.
MENEHUNE JUICE
This lighthearted libation creates the right mood for Menehune watching.
A rainbow of Polynesian flavors combines with
fine light rum to set the stage.

PINEAPPLE AND COTTAGE CHEESE SALAD
A delightful combination of Hawaiian fruit, cottage cheese, carrots, tuna

Your Choice of
BAKED LASAGNE NAPOLETANA
We know you'll enjoy this dish. Layers of egg pasta, imported ricotta and
mozzarella cheeses and a meaty tomato sauce. That's Italian!
THE CHEF'S SPECIALTY
MAHI MAHI SAUTE MEUNIERE
Tender, white filets of Mahi Mahi selected from cold Pacific waters are
seasoned, dipped in flour and whipped egg and sauteed to a golden
brown. An herbed butter sauce accents this selection.
BRAISED SHORT RIBS OF BEEF PLANTATION STYLE
Boneless ribs of USDA Choice beef are braised until "fork-tender" in a
ren and suory spicy brown sauce.
